    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single standardized ASTM F1717 test configuration; this shortfall is accepted given regulatory standardization of test conditions and corroborating inter-laboratory agreement. All QoI comparisons satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% acceptance bounds across both laboratories. Overall credibility sufficient to support Medium assurance level for model risk level 3 COU. Package accepted for regulatory submission.",
